Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.66,0:07:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H894138&\pos(310,363)}Yamazaki, thinking the camera is off, expresses what's on his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.66,0:07:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,After a while, the effects of the alcohol starts kicking in and Yamazaki, not realizing the camera is still rolling,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.06,0:07:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,starts talking about Downtown and other topics.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:55.74,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Amazing. Just amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:07:59.48,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Those 2 (Downtown) are really amazing, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.51,0:08:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,In what way?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.91,0:08:03.71,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,You know, when I first saw their manzai, I thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:07.28,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,"Wow, these {\i1}dudes{\i0} are gonna be the kings."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.12,0:08:16.46,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Yeah, when I first saw them, I didn't know them at all, when I first saw Downtown, I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.49,0:08:20.50,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,"These {\i1}dudes{\i0} are gonna be the kings" and now look, they're at the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.66,0:08:23.63,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,I have a sixth sense for these kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.63,0:08:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Recently, you know, Hamada-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.70,0:08:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't he dye his hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.04,0:08:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.51,0:08:35.74,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,What do I think, well, I was surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:40.98,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Because... "If you dye your hair, you're garbage!" is what he's been saying for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.98,0:08:44.02,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,So now, he's become garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.15,0:08:45.55,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,That is just garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.19,0:08:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, after enduring the long 14 hour flight, the plane has landed in Rome. Yama-chan is still in his Arare-chan outfit and his number 1 priority is to seek out spaghetti!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:09:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(248,97)\fade(100,100)\3c&H60AD8A&}Leonardo da Vinci Airport
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:01.10,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,We made it. Italy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.13,0:09:03.87,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,100)}Looks like we finally made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.94,0:09:06.94,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,That was crazy, too intense. Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.14,0:09:09.31,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,I didn't even get to sleep at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:11.91,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Pizza, let's go get that pizza.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.91,0:09:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Pizza?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:14.61,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(324,389)}Yeah, pizza. Oh wait, not pizza, spaghetti.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.84,0:09:22.59,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,We made it, we're here in Italy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.19,0:09:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.19,0:09:26.19,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(316,404)}Is this the city of Rome?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.46,0:09:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.66,0:09:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So he said the heel, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.53,0:09:34.40,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,No way, we shouldn't have to bother with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.93,0:09:38.44,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,We made it all the way here. Let's just buy it in Italy and go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.91,0:09:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But Macchan said the heel, so we need to go all the way over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.84,0:09:47.88,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,100)}Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.18,0:09:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll need to board another plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.08,0:09:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... For reals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:50.98,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(318,397)}For reals?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.25,0:09:53.25,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Whaaaat... No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.75,0:10:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,From the airport in Rome, Yamazaki takes a domestic flight, yet again in economy class, to the city that faces the Adriatic Sea, Bari.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-stop traveling since the morning has caused
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.26,0:10:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(317,413)\fade(100,100)\3c&H894138&}Yamazaki sleeping like a corpse
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.03,0:10:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamazaki unable to hide his exhaustion
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and is now sleeping soundly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:12.07,Yamasaki,,0,310,0,,{\fade(0,100)}We're here,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.70,0:10:12.07,Yamasaki,,0,60,0,,{\fade(0,100)}we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:12.07,Yamasaki,,250,0,0,,{\fade(0,100)}We've made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.44,0:10:14.44,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's all dark now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.60,0:10:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(487,367)\fade(100,100\3c&H07AFA4&}Time in Italy: 10 PM
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:16.17,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,It's so dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.57,0:10:17.44,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Okay so... So now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.58,0:10:18.58,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Um... the heel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.61,0:10:19.88,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Um... What was it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.88,0:10:21.78,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Let's just buy spaghetti and go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.45,0:10:24.45,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(325,376)}Why can't I just do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is called Bari.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.72,0:10:28.72,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,397)}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Bari.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.09,0:10:30.65,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,The heel of the boot, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.72,0:10:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We're still only at the achilles heel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.22,0:10:35.03,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Archilles heel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.76,0:10:42.10,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,We have to ride in a car again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.53,0:10:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\clip(152,379,178,407)\t(0,1500,\clip(152,379,578,407))}We'll be traveling by car now~{\pos(313,407)}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:44.63,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,For about how long?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.67,0:10:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(313,378)}Uhh, for about 2 hours. I hear.{\pos(313,407)}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.57,0:10:46.56,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,2 hours?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.57,0:10:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,By car.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.10,0:10:50.71,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,{\clip(245,442,264,470)\t(0,2500,\clip(245,442,664,470))}So damn far!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.17,0:10:55.28,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Because I mean... We've been going...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.28,0:10:58.05,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,For 20 hours. We've been traveling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:10:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.75,0:11:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,6am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.32,0:11:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,In Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.62,0:11:04.62,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(318,391)}In Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.15,0:11:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.69,0:11:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,406)}We had you come in to Nihon TV at around 6:30am so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.69,0:11:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been right about 24 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.56,0:11:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,After arriving in Bari, Yamazaki immediately resumes travel by car.  He heads towards his destination, the city at the "heel," Lecce.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.97,0:11:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,From Bari to Lecce, the distance is about 200km.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,His journey still continues to attain spaghetti in Italy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.97,0:11:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,415)\fade(100,100)\3c&H894138&}Traveling the distance of 200km by car.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.98,0:11:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(323,413)\fade(100,100)\3c&H000000&\3c&H894138&}Yamazaki, sound asleep, again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.21,0:11:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Around this time, Yamazaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.22,0:11:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,with so much international traveling, is dead asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.75,0:11:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The city he seeks is Lecce.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.43,0:11:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A city that gleams in bronze light and one of the most beautiful and aesthetic cities in Southern Italy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been 24 hours since starting the journey from Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.89,0:11:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(326,407)\fade(100,100)\3c&H894138&}The car takes them to the heart of Lecce city.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.50,0:11:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamazaki, though falling apart from fatigue, finally sets foot in the final destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.74,0:12:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\clip(194,444,218,469)\t(0,2300,\clip(194,444,618,469))}We've arrived in Lecce!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:12:00.67,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,399)}We've made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.81,0:12:05.81,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,We've finally made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.91,0:12:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,411)\fade(100,100)\3c&H894138&}4 hours is all he's allowed in Lecce.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.75,0:12:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamazaki is only allowed 4 hours in Lecce.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Within this time, he must attain the spaghetti.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.49,0:12:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamazaki hurries in search of a restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.49,0:12:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.70,0:12:23.76,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.76,0:12:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.76,0:12:25.76,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Is this a restaurant? This?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,401)\fade(0,100){\3c&H4338C8&}Spotted a restaurant!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.13,0:12:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Immediately, they spot a restaurant-looking establishment!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(323,372)\fade(100,100){\3c&H894138&}Yamazaki is handed an Italian language cheatsheet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,In order for Yamazaki to make the purchase, they give him a note of Italian translations on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.51,0:12:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,369)\fade(100,100)\3c&H894138&}And his task is to order a spaghetti with no meat in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.91,0:12:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Bringing meat to Japan from a foreign country is incredibly complicated, so he must order a spaghetti with no meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Can Yamazaki procure this spaghetti without a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.22,0:12:50.29,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.26,0:12:52.26,Italian,,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,410)}Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.69,0:12:52.69,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.93,0:12:58.36,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,I come from Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.87,0:13:03.00,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,There's something I'd like to order.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:05.04,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.77,0:13:10.91,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,I'd like to order a plate of spaghetti.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:13.65,Italian,,0,0,0,,We're already closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.65,0:13:16.85,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,I'll pay for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.18,0:13:17.78,Italian,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.32,0:13:20.75,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,I'll pay for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.75,0:13:23.99,Italian,,0,0,0,,The kitchen is all closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.99,0:13:27.26,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Please make it a spaghetti with no meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.26,0:13:30.46,Italian,,0,0,0,,We're completely closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.46,0:13:31.60,Italian,,0,0,0,,We're not open.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They said they're closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:33.10,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.00,0:13:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They said they're closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.73,0:13:36.17,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(319,391)}Closed? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.17,0:13:37.67,Italian,,0,0,0,,We're closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:38.87,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,No No No No No
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.87,0:13:40.67,Italian,,0,0,0,,Yes Yes Yes Yes Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(318,418)}"Si" is Italian for "yes."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.07,0:13:46.61,Italian,,0,0,0,,We don't have any food right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.78,0:13:47.51,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.91,0:13:49.15,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Why why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.58,0:13:50.78,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.65,0:13:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They said they're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.29,0:13:57.95,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.95,0:13:59.42,Italian,,0,0,0,,Good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.82,0:14:00.82,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,413)}Good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.16,0:14:03.16,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Why are they closed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go search for another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.23,0:14:13.44,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Why are they closed...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.43,0:14:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,388)}Because it's already past midnight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.44,0:14:15.87,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,That can't be the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:20.51,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,The cuckoos are chirping and they're just doing nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(327,413)\fade(100,100,)\3c&H894138&}They drive around by car in search for the next restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamazaki, thinking he could quickly order and go home,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,was refused and is searching for the next restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.28,0:14:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But because it's so late at night, they aren't able to find another one so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, they find the next restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.29,0:14:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamazaki approaches, in hopes of ordering.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(326,416)\fade(100,100,)\3c&H894138&}Ordering from the second restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:41.33,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Nchao!*
