Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.50,0:14:50.20,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Closed Closed Closed Closed
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:51.71,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,No No No No No
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.71,0:14:52.87,Italian,,0,0,0,,Yes Yes Yes Yes Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.01,0:14:59.28,Italian,,0,0,0,,Don't take it personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.68,0:15:01.68,Italian,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.05,0:15:04.05,Italian,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:08.72,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.96,0:15:11.43,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,It's not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.36,0:15:16.83,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,They're not open!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.83,0:15:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:20.27,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,It's late but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:22.27,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,But we left at 6:30 in Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.87,0:15:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,390)}We're just barely late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:23.44,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The restaurant is still open, but they're not serving spaghetti anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:28.88,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,What do you mean they're not serving spaghetti, that's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.08,0:15:30.28,Hamada,,0,0,0,,{\pos(483.338,376)}You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.14,0:15:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(316,369)\fade(100,100)\3c&H894138&}After that, Yamazaki wanders around the town of Lecce by foot for about an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.14,0:15:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, Yamazaki walks around Lecce in the middle of the night, looking for information on a restaurant that's still open.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.55,0:15:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But unable to get any promising answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.36,0:15:45.02,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.89,0:15:50.83,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,We don't have much time left until we have to go back home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.86,0:15:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We have only about 3 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.86,0:15:53.33,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(322,396)}Whaaaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.53,0:15:56.47,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Geez, this pisses me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.31,0:16:01.77,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Oh, this place is a restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.11,0:16:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(328,405)\fade(0,100)\3c&H4338C8&}Spotted another restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.08,0:16:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, Yamazaki spots the third restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.51,0:16:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,However, will Yamazaki be able to order spaghetti?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:16.12,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:17.32,Italian,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:22.56,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,I'd like to order a plate of spaghetti.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.80,0:16:27.90,Italian,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:30.87,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,No?! Why why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.67,0:16:36.34,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Please make it a spaghetti with no meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.81,0:16:39.24,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,{\pos(504,446)}You're still ordering? \NYou just keep going, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.21,0:16:41.95,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Please, I beg of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.28,0:16:44.62,Italian,,0,0,0,,Beg of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:56.19,Translator's Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(314,54)}*Translator's Note: Apparently, Bingo Bongo is a movie that is the comedic Italian equivalent of Tarzan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:50.62,Italian,,0,0,0,,What is that? Is that Bingo Bongo?*
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.62,0:16:52.32,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Bingo Bongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:54.66,Italian,,0,0,0,,Bingo Bongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.29,0:17:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason, the restaurant staff are amused by Gacchan and ask the chef to make an order of spaghetti.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.46,0:16:58.46,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(300,142)}Thank you! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.90,0:17:04.10,Italian,,0,0,0,,Pippo, make an order of spaghetti for Japan, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.44,0:17:09.11,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.41,0:17:14.24,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,I'd like to order a plate of spaghetti.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:16.85,Italian,,0,0,0,,We've already done the cleaning, we're closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.25,0:17:17.98,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.98,0:17:19.58,Italian,,0,0,0,,We're closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.05,0:17:22.49,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Please, I beg of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.49,0:17:24.99,Italian,,0,0,0,,We don't have anymore spaghetti.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.45,0:17:26.66,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.66,0:17:27.19,Italian,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.52,0:17:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Will Yamazaki ever be able to get his hands on some spaghetti?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.76,0:17:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There, an older gentleman who looks to be the owner, reaches out to Yamazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.44,0:17:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He says to make do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:42.40,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Make do with this? No no no.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.40,0:17:45.41,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,I'd like a plate of spaghetti with no meat, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.77,0:17:49.11,Italian,,0,0,0,,A plate of spaghetti with no meat, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.28,0:17:51.28,Italian,,0,0,0,,Come back tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.05,0:17:51.45,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,414)}You don't have any?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.32,0:17:55.72,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,We don't have time to come back tomorrow. We're on a time limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.72,0:17:59.95,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(328,351)\clip(247,317,269,349)\t(0,3000,\clip(247,317,669,349))}No time limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.89,0:17:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(319,418)}(I have unlimited time.)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.85,0:18:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly, the old gentleman...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.32,0:18:05.29,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,What's this? Boil it! This is no good, boil it for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.29,0:18:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They bring him a package of dried pasta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.97,0:18:14.37,Italian,,0,0,0,,1 piece of spaghetti for 1,000,000 lira*
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.13,0:18:16.17,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,372)}No! Expensive, too expensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.97,0:18:16.50,Translator's Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(316,50)}Translator's notes: Lira was the form of currency before Italy changed to Euros. 1,000,000 lira = 60,000 yen = roughly USD $600
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.54,0:18:18.77,Italian,,0,0,0,,2 pieces of spaghetti for 2,000,000 lira*
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.54,0:18:18.77,Translator's Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(323,29)}*Translator's notes: 120,000 yen = roughly USD $1,200
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.77,0:18:20.94,Italian,,0,0,0,,3 pieces of spaghetti for 3,000,000 lira*
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.77,0:18:20.94,Translator's Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(325,50)}*Translator's notes: 180,000 yen = roughly USD $1,800
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.94,0:18:24.31,Italian,,0,0,0,,Do you want 1 piece of spaghetti for 1,000,000 lira?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.71,0:18:24.48,Yamasaki,,0,0,70,,That's so expensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.65,0:18:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(334,280)\t(0,6000,\fscx130\fscy130)\fs36}The prices for spaghetti are incredibly inflated, \Nwhat will Yamazaki do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.91,0:18:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The price for spaghetti has been incredibly increased! This Italian man is be feared! Is what we thought, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.32,0:18:31.65,Italian,,0,0,0,,Well, let's make it for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.32,0:18:38.86,Italian,,0,0,0,,Let's treat Japan to a plate of spaghetti.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.86,0:18:40.86,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.36,0:18:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He says he'll treat us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.06,0:18:46.17,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Treat us? You will treat us? Oh, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:50.27,Italian,,0,0,0,,Let's give this spaghetti to this child (Gacchan).
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:53.27,Italian,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,100)}Let's give a friendly applause for Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.88,0:19:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(329,418)\fade(100,0)\3c&H894138&}Yamazaki has no idea what's going on with the strange turn of events.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.35,0:19:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\move(818,385,340,385,18,300)\3c&H24B863&\c&H0C468F&}In the midst of cooking spaghetti.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\move(340,385,-200,385,25,300)\3c&H24B863&\c&H0C468F&}In the midst of cooking spaghetti.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.25,0:19:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,At the words of a lively saint, Yamazaki is finally able to get spaghetti.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.75,0:19:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,At this time, they're cooking a Lecce style spaghetti with parmesan cheese and basil in a tomato-based sauce, no meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.36,0:19:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They make spaghetti for Yamazaki as representatives of Southern Italian cuisine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:20.87,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,They're making a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.17,0:19:29.01,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you!! Thank you, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(329,112)\fade(0,100)\c&H379BFA&}Yamazaki acquires spaghetti!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.11,0:19:33.61,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,It's done!! It's here, the spaghetti is finally made!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.81,0:19:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to this kind saint, Yamazaki is miraculously able to acquire the spaghetti he needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.15,0:19:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,As Yamazaki departs, the restaurant bids us a warm Italian farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.52,0:19:47.83,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,{\clip(176,441,184,471)\t(0,1500,\clip(176,441,584,471))}I've acquired the spaghetti!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.13,0:19:50.76,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(230,473)}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:50.76,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(413,473)}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.43,0:19:56.43,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Yeah! We got the spaghetti!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.80,0:20:00.30,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,This spaghetti looks so delicious. I'm so touched. This here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.50,0:20:06.61,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,100)}I'll bring this back to Japan and let's all eat this with everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.48,0:20:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,After acquiring this earnest plate of spaghetti, Yamazaki travels another 24 hours just like before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.55,0:20:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And makes his way straight back to Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.23,0:20:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(315,410)\fade(100,100)}Yamazaki's spaghetti that \N he bought home from Lecce
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.90,0:20:36.14,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,This is really
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.14,0:20:37.81,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,authentically Italian.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.81,0:20:41.34,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,It was kept frozen
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.34,0:20:43.11,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,and naturally thawed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.35,0:20:46.62,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That's no good, it's like a sherbet then!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.05,0:20:49.08,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Then by microwave...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.25,0:20:50.42,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Eh? You put it in the microwave?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.08,0:20:51.08,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Yes, please heat it up in the microwave.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.42,0:20:52.42,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Ughhh, I don't want it anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.55,0:20:54.55,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,No way, you can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.62,0:20:56.62,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,This is that spaghetti, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.86,0:20:57.86,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is the spaghetti.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.62,0:20:58.63,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.86,0:21:01.23,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is really it! That's the real thing! So I told them not make a replacement.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.23,0:21:07.97,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,That is absolutely unforgivable, I told them I will definitely bring you guys the exact dish that was given.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.97,0:21:10.24,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I don't understand what the hell you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:13.11,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,How did you freeze it then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.17,0:21:15.34,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,I froze it over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.38,0:21:17.38,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "over there?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.38,0:21:17.38,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "over there?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.61,0:21:18.08,Endo,,0,0,0,,Where is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.48,0:21:20.21,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,What the hell do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:21.62,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,In Italy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.15,0:21:24.22,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That made no sense at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.89,0:21:25.89,Endo,,0,0,0,,Okay, it's ready now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.19,0:21:27.19,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,It's done now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.06,0:21:30.06,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,See, now it's warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.06,0:21:33.73,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Well... I'm not so sure about the inside though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.73,0:21:33.73,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.99,0:21:36.93,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Regardless, Hamada is going to inhale all of this in one go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.96,0:21:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.54,0:21:44.14,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you saying? Come on everyone, eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.11,0:21:47.11,Endo,,0,0,0,,It's all stuck together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.37,0:21:48.88,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,This is no good. I don't want to eat this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.21,0:21:50.21,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Come on, eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.04,0:21:52.78,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I guess we should have a little. Hurry up and eat it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.88,0:21:54.01,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.92,0:21:59.92,Endo,,0,0,0,,I'll help myself then.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.29,0:22:05.29,Hamada,,0,0,0,,This has no flavor at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.29,0:22:07.29,Endo,,0,0,0,,This is gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.39,0:22:08.16,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.46,0:22:10.46,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Eat all of it please, eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.63,0:22:11.66,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,No, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.16,0:22:13.16,Hamada,,0,0,0,,No, you're the one who should eat all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.07,0:22:12.63,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.63,0:22:14.43,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.50,0:22:16.50,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.07,0:22:18.07,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Why did you change from casual to polite?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.97,0:22:20.34,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You eat it. Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.97,0:22:22.97,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.71,0:22:25.81,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,See, you're so harsh with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.81,0:22:27.58,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Isn't it odd that it's only me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.58,0:22:29.62,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one who gets hit like this! Ow ow ow ow ow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.62,0:22:32.02,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Why are you pinching me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.02,0:22:34.89,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,That hurts, geez... Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.92,0:22:36.92,Endo,,0,0,0,,This is just weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.56,0:22:38.56,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You're not even scooping anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.92,0:22:39.09,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It's all dry and crumbly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.66,0:22:41.06,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.42,0:22:41.42,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Why only that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.76,0:22:44.76,Hamada,,0,0,0,,This isn't even funny, so take this off.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.90,0:22:51.37,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It tastes bad, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.70,0:22:52.70,Endo,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.70,0:22:52.70,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.47,0:22:53.47,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.87,0:22:55.87,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto, give him this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.07,0:22:57.07,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Oh, we have some condiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.51,0:22:59.51,Hamada,,0,0,0,,For the occasion, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.11,0:22:59.81,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Condiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.04,0:23:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll improve the taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.05,0:23:03.68,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Let's add some flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.31,0:23:04.31,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,There's no way I can eat this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.05,0:23:06.72,Endo,,0,0,0,,Tabasco.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.72,0:23:08.82,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I will add dashes of this... To the back of your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.12,0:23:19.73,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Please, no, please!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.33,0:23:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, the flavor will be improved.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.73,0:23:21.73,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Your way of thinking will be improved.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.47,0:23:22.87,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.47,0:23:22.87,Endo,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.67,0:23:26.20,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Is this going to be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.27,0:23:27.47,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Isn't it written on the label?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.47,0:23:29.47,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's okay, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.94,0:23:31.07,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Why would that be written on the label? To not pour this on one's head?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.14,0:23:35.85,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It says "Only for use on the back of the head."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.50,0:23:37.75,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Those are the instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.25,0:23:40.22,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Wait wait, it actually says, "For use on the back of the head."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.48,0:23:43.22,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,That's the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.05,0:23:44.99,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It's one of the many purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.02,0:23:46.52,Endo,,0,0,0,,It's definitely okay to pour.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.69,0:23:48.69,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Hold on a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.42,0:23:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.83,0:23:50.83,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Massage that area for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.96,0:23:54.56,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What the hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.53,0:23:55.53,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Am I going to be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.56,0:23:56.56,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,What kind of situation has this developed into?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.77,0:23:58.77,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I'm going to soak his scalp.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.60,0:24:02.60,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Oh that seems pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.37,0:24:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's applied very nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.77,0:24:04.24,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Eat it, eat it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.44,0:24:07.44,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Hurry, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.14,0:24:08.98,Endo,,0,0,0,,Do your best! Do your best!
